<h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>

<p>An Inventory integration will allow you to configure Product price and inventory availability in Endless Aisle.</p>

<p><strong>Figure 1</strong>: Illustrates a Product Detail View in Endless Aisle</p>

<p><img src="http://localhost:4006//images/ea-product-detail.png" alt="Endless Aisle Product Detail" /></p>

<p>The table below lists where each component comes from and how to modify it, where possible:</p>

<p><strong>Table 1:</strong> Source for each component of Figure 5</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
